        It deletes the ReLUOp from `ReLU -> FakeQuantize` if the FakeQuantizeOp has input_low > 0.
        It deletes the ClampOp from `Clamp -> FakeQuantize` if the FakeQuantizeOp has input ranges smaller then Clamp limits.
